{
  "stem": "14867.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was some kind of problem there because his daughter-in-law mar-- was Polish, the Major's daughter-in-law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she insisted upon bringing him up as a Polish kid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His son was in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never knew if he was in the Polish army or the German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was never told, and I never found out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he didn't care for his sis-- for his daughter-in-law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he really wanted someone else who will be-- of course, he was too good to play with the peasants.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He liked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That I will be able to play and study with him together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That a Polish girl had run away from home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not run away, run away from Poland because there was no job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't get a job in Poland, and everybody was running to other parts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the way, I got so tired I decided to see if I can get a job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody told me I can find a job here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't tell them that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I clean myself up?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even know where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't even remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe I cleaned myself up before I entered his place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because this is not a thing that is-- that's unusual, because a lot of Polish girls ran away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no jobs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a lot of Polish girls ran to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not everybody could get official-- an official train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the transportation wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody was running all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's not that here's an unusual thing, somebody came to look for a job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure he had tens and tens of girls who came to look for jobs there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, even the servants were not shocked to see that somebody is coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that wasn't unusual.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
